com.esri.svr.cat
Class BaseCatalog

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--com.esri.svr.cat.BaseCatalog
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
ServiceCatalog, ServiceCatalogBean
public abstract class BaseCatalog
extends Object
implements Serializable

This class provides a base functionality for managing a service information described by an AXL file. Currently it only supports the image service.
